      "html": "<p>“开放纹理的粗棉布”，1650年代，最初是用于压制凝乳的布料，源自于 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cheese \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cheese\">cheese</a>（n.1）+ <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cloth \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cloth\">cloth</a>。</p>"
